{"type":"message","id":"dbdc5510","parentId":"232b0d05","timestamp":"2026-04-02T09:31:53.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7b38XPDdlPOFJXya1Y0C9k0W|fc_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce377da9bc81909acb0c490b6b9817","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Research `openclaw-nerve` and alternative mission-control / observability options for OpenClaw. Focus on: (1) what openclaw-nerve actually does, install requirements, risks, and whether it would help monitor background runs like PM->VO->S1; (2) what other options exist for mission control / observability in the OpenClaw ecosystem or adjacent community usage; (3) what the community/docs/repo discussions say about usefulness, limitations, stability, and fit for real operator workflows. Prefer official docs/repo/issues/discussions first, then recent community evidence. Produce a concise but technically grounded comparison and recommendation for Lucca. Do not install anything; research only.","label":"haiku-nerve-research","agentId":"haiku","runtime":"subagent","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":900,"timeoutSeconds":900,"cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace","streamTo":"parent"},"partialJson":"{\"task\":\"Research `openclaw-nerve` and alternative mission-control / observability options for OpenClaw. Focus on: (1) what openclaw-nerve actually does, install requirements, risks, and whether it would help monitor background runs like PM->VO->S1; (2) what other options exist for mission control / observability in the OpenClaw ecosystem or adjacent community usage; (3) what the community/docs/repo discussions say about usefulness, limitations, stability, and fit for real operator workflows. Prefer official docs/repo/issues/discussions first, then recent community evidence. Produce a concise but technically grounded comparison and recommendation for Lucca. Do not install anything; research only.\",\"label\":\"haiku-nerve-research\",\"agentId\":\"haiku\",\"runtime\":\"subagent\",\"mo