{"type":"message","id":"690370b7","parentId":"796c1933","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:21:44.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Tailscale é basicamente uma forma de aceder remotamente às tuas máquinas por uma **rede privada segura**, como se todas estivessem na mesma LAN, mesmo estando em sítios diferentes.\n\n### Em termos práticos\nSe escolhesses Tailscale:\n- podias abrir o Nerve de outro device teu\n- sem expor a interface publicamente na internet\n- usando o IP privado da tua tailnet\n\n### As opções aí significam:\n- **This machine only (localhost)**  \n  Só abre no teu próprio PC. Mais simples e mais seguro.\n\n- **Via Tailscale tailnet IP**  \n  Abres noutro device teu através da rede privada do Tailscale.\n\n- **Via Tailscale Serve**  \n  Variante mais “polida” do Tailscale para servir a app.\n\n- **From other devices on my network**  \n  Expor para a tua rede local/LAN.\n\n- **Custom setup**  \n  Manual / avançado.\n\n### O que eu recomendo agora\nComo primeiro setup, escolhe:\n\n**`This machine only (localhost)`**\n\nPorque:\n- é o mais simples\n- o mais seguro\n- reduz variáveis\n- primeiro validamos o Nerve a funcionar, depois se quiseres abrimos remoto com Tailscale\n\nEntão podes só dar **Enter** nessa opção.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce51432f4481908371947b2f31eddd\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":351,"output":286,"cacheRead":153856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":154493,"cost":{"input":0.0008775,"output":0.00429,"cacheRead":0.038464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0436315}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775128896450,"responseId":"resp_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce514207ac819096759d3179c3c3ed"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d173ee8d","parentId":"690370b7","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:29:11.524Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-02 08:29 GMT-3] √ Agent display name Tobias\n │\n ● How will you access Nerve? [3/6]\n │\n√ How will you connect to Nerve? This machine only (localhost)\n │ ✓ Nerve will be available at http://localhost:3080\n │\n ● Text-to-Speech (optional) [5/6]\n │\n │ Edge TTS is always available (free, no API key needed).\n │ Add API keys below for higher-quality alternatives.\n\n√ OpenAI API Key (press Enter to skip)\n√ Replicate API Token (press Enter to skip)\n │\n ● Advanced Settings (optional) [6/6]\n │\n√ Customize file paths? (most users should skip this) No\n\n │ ✓ Configuration written to .env\n │ ✓ Installed 1 bundled skill to C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\n\n ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │ Gateway http://127.0.0.1:18789 │\n │ Agent Tobias │\n │ HTTP :3080 │\n │ TTS Edge (free) │\n │ Host 127.0.0.1 (local only) │\n │ Auth Disabled │\n └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n Next steps:\n Development: npm run dev && npm run dev:server\n Production: npm run prod\n\n Open http://localhost:3080 in your browser.\n\n Deployment guides:\n Run everything on one machine: https://docs.nerve.zone/guide/deployment-local\n Use a cloud Gateway with Nerve on your laptop: https://docs.nerve.zone/guide/deployment-remote-gateway\n Run both Nerve and Gateway in the cloud: https://docs.nerve.zone/guide/deployment-cloud\n\nPS C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\openclaw-nerve>"}],"timestamp":1775129351502}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cb1b06e","parentId":"d173ee8d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T11:29:20.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfeito — **o setup terminou com sucesso**.\n\n## Como abrir\nO Nerve vai abrir aqui:\n\n```text\nhttp://localhost:3080\n```\n\n## Estado do setup\nFicou assim:\n- **Gateway:** `http://127.0.0.1:18789`\n- **Agent:** `Tobias`\n- **Host:** `127.0.0.1`\n- **Modo:** local only\n- **Auth:** disabled\n- **TTS:** Edge (free)\n\n## O que falta agora\nSó falta **ligar o Nerve**.\n\nNo teu PowerShell, ainda dentro da pasta `openclaw-nerve`, corre:\n\n```powershell\nnpm run prod\n```\n\nDepois disso:\n- deixa o processo a correr\n- abre no browser:\n  ```text\n  http://localhost:3080\n  ```\n\n## Resumo curto\n1. setup feito ✅\n2. correr:\n   ```powershell\n   npm run prod\n   ```\n3. abrir:\n   ```text\n   http://localhost:3080\n   ```\n\nSe quiser, depois que abrires, eu posso guiar-te nos **primeiros 3 checks** lá dentro para validar se está tudo a falar bem com o gateway.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce530b73708190bd8b8f2fa14fcdd1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":561,"output":272,"cacheRead":154368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155201,"cost":{"input":0.0014025,"output":0.00408,"cacheRead":0.038592,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0440745}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775129351519,"responseId":"resp_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce530921d88190a2cd52b05dd7b751"}}
