{"type":"message","id":"0cf8f3fd","parentId":"d41e3928","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:02:05.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Faz no **PowerShell**, exactamente onde tu já estás.\n\nCopia e cola **estas duas linhas**:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw config set tools.exec.security full\nopenclaw config set tools.exec.ask off\n```\n\nDepois confirma com:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw config get tools.exec\n```\n\n### Em resumo\nNo teu terminal PowerShell, faz isto tudo:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw config set tools.exec.security full\nopenclaw config set tools.exec.ask off\nopenclaw config get tools.exec\n```\n\nE manda-me o output final.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce5abadc7881908ab0a682660ca136\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":266,"output":130,"cacheRead":170880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":171276,"cost":{"input":0.000665,"output":0.0019500000000000001,"cacheRead":0.04272,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.045335}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775131318044,"responseId":"resp_0408171ee7a64bae0169ce5ab7260881908f04aa36a0d82423"}}
